Welcome to the VERY FIRST edition of TIER FACTOR! In this very special episode of the Major Issues Podcast The Don and Yogi go over Batman's cinematic rogue's gallery to determine each one's overall ranking! Who is the cream of the crop? Who will be left in the dust? All those questions will be answered and MORE In this INAUGURAL edition of TIER FACTOR presented by Comic Book Clique! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

